Senate State and Local Government 1
Amendment No. 1 to SB0815
Briggs
Signature of Sponsor
AMEND S e nate Bill No. 815 House Bill No. 725*
by adding the following new section immediately preceding the last section and renumbering the
subsequent section accordingly:
Section ___. Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 7, Chapter 40, is amended by adding
the following as a new section:
Notwithstanding any other deadline for the completion of an economic
development project or extraordinary retail or tourism facility project, the deadline for the
completion of such projects is May 1, 2027 in cities having a population of not less than
twenty-seven thousand one hundred forty (27,140) nor more than twenty-seven
thousand one hundred fifty (27,150) and a population of not less than fifty-five thousand
four hundred forty (55,440) nor more than fifty-five thousand four hundred fifty (55,450)
that are located in a county having a population of not less than one hundred fifty-eight
thousand one hundred (158,100) nor more than one hundred fifty-eight thousand two
hundred (158,200) according to the 2020 federal census or any subsequent federal
census.
